# [DOMAIN NAME] - Log

> Historical record. Completed work rotates here from Recently Completed (5+ items).
> You rarely need to read this - it's an archive. Claude only reads it when you ask.
>
> **Per-type rotation naming:**
> - `dev`: `{DOMAIN}_LOG_{project-slug}.md` per project (e.g., `DEV_LOG_auth-refactor.md`)
> - `ops`: `{DOMAIN}_LOG_YYYY-QN.md` per quarter (e.g., `FINANCES_LOG_2026-Q2.md`)
> - `journaling`: `{DOMAIN}_LOG_YYYY-MM.md` per month (e.g., `CYRUS_LOG_2026-04.md`)
> - `reference` / `ephemeral`: single LOG file is fine - low rotation volume

